职责\\n\\n负责用户身份认证：手机号注册/登录、JWT 发放与刷新、登出。\\n\\n## 流程
图\\n\\n```mermaid\\nsequenceDiagram\\n    participant C as Flutter App\\n    pa
rticipant API as AuthController\\n    participant S as AuthService\\n    partici
pant DB as MySQL\\n    participant R as Redis\\n\\n    C->>API: POST /auth/login
(phone, sms_code)\\n    API->>S: validateSmsCode()\\n    S->>R: get sms_code:pho
ne\\n    R-->>S: code\\n    S->>DB: findOrCreateUser(phone)\\n    DB-->>S: User\
\n    S->>S: generateTokens(userId)\\n    S-->>API: {accessToken, refreshToken}\
\n    API-->>C: 200 OK\\n```\\n\\n## 关键文件\\n\\n| 文件 | 路径 |\\n|------|---
---|\\n| Controller | `apps/api/src/modules/auth/auth.controller.ts` |\\n| Servi
ce | `apps/api/src/modules/auth/auth.service.ts` |\\n| DTO | `apps/api/src/modul
es/auth/dto/` |\\n| Guard | `apps/api/src/common/guards/jwt-auth.guard.ts` |\\n|
Exception Filter | `apps/api/src/common/filters/all-exceptions.filter.ts` |\\n| 
Current User Decorator | `apps/api/src/common/decorators/current-user.decorator.
ts` |\\n| User Entity | `apps/api/src/modules/auth/entities/user.entity.ts` |\\n
| User Profile Entity | `apps/api/src/modules/auth/entities/user-profile.entity.
ts` |\\n| Migration | `apps/api/src/database/migrations/20250410000000-CreateUse
rsAndUserProfiles.ts` |\\n| Service Tests | `apps/api/src/modules/auth/tests/aut
h.service.spec.ts` |\\n| Flutter BLoC | `apps/mobile/lib/presentation/blocs/auth
/` |\\n| Flutter Login Page | `apps/mobile/lib/presentation/pages/login_page.dar
t` |\\n| Flutter Secure Storage | `apps/mobile/lib/core/storage/secure_storage.d
art` |\\n| Flutter Auth Interceptor | `apps/mobile/lib/core/network/auth_interce
ptor.dart` |\\n| Shared Types | `packages/shared-types/src/index.ts` |\\n\\n## 
认证状态机\\n\\n- `unauthenticated`：未登录\\n- `authenticating`：登录中\\n- `au
thenticated`：已登录（持有 accessToken）\\n- `tokenRefreshing`：Token 刷新中\\n\
